WEBVTT

00:14:28.413 --> 00:14:32.635
Or do you think that a large number
of Muslim women actually feel resentful

00:14:32.659 --> 00:14:37.033
that they have restrictions that men
don't seem to have in the same way?

00:14:37.057 --> 00:14:40.609
They may have other restrictions,
but not in the way they dress.

00:14:40.633 --> 00:14:42.663
DM: So it's a really good question, Chris.

00:14:42.687 --> 00:14:44.445
I would say that there are --

00:14:44.469 --> 00:14:48.069
I can never dismiss that some
women do feel this way.

00:14:48.093 --> 00:14:52.642
But according to a study
that we just published

00:14:52.666 --> 00:14:55.171
at the Institute for Social Policy
and Understanding,

00:14:55.195 --> 00:15:01.000
